Title: azure: Fix app registration crashing while parsing agent output
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1727782634
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p35

When using a <code>|</code> symbol in the display name of an azure app, the
azure_app_registration check would fail with
<code>WARNING: Parsing of section azure_app_registration failed - please submit a crash report!</code>.

With this werk, we fix this error and support the <code>|</code> symbol in the
display name of azure apps.

<strong>User action required</strong>

To apply the fix, you need to rediscover the <code>azure_app_registration</code>
services.
